measurements.description: Ten flowers and six buds on three up to 12-cm inflorescences; dorsal sepal ovate, white overlaid light green basally, horizontally barred lavender proximally some flowers; lateral sepals white, overlaid light green, horizontal dark lavender bars; petals ovate white overlaid light green; lip spatulate, white, overlaid lavender centrally, stippled and spotted lavender distally; column white, anther cap whiate; substance firm; texture diamond dust.
